document_data.History:
Elthaulin was leading a rite at the [[Dark Shrine]] in [[Zhentil Keep]] before Shandril's arrival, which was cut short by Fzoul Chembryl; Elthaulin resented this immensely. He didn't notice, but his rite resulted in a genuine sign from [[Bane]].{{cite book/Crown of Fire/TPB 2002|306-307|19}}

While Shandril was on her way to fighting Fzoul Chembryl, Elthaulin began to gather the priests loyal to him through [[Neaveil]] and [[Oprion Blackstone]], commanding they find all priests more loyal to him than to Fzoul.{{cite book/Crown of Fire/TPB 2002|312-313|20}}

Elthaulin tried to lead priests into battle against Shandril after she slew Fzoul; she ignored his forces and focused her efforts on him first, killing him instantly.
